  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7609301">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7609301/" class="title-link">民主化带来种族屠杀？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7609301"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/thucydides/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2316203-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/thucydides/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">阿修</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-27"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-27 09:20:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7609301_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在多民族国家，民主化如何可能？自约翰•密尔以降，许多社会科学家都共同关注过这一问题。众人皆知，在民主化转型过程中，很容易出现下列情况：一、国家控制能力变弱；二、政客诉诸民族感情、利益对社会下层进行政治动员；三、政客攀比（outbidding），竞相向极端思想、政策...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7609301/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">24有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7609301_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7609301_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7558420">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7558420/" class="title-link">多数人的暴政</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7558420"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1679535-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/" class="author">
